      // /manifest — FID-006 v3 Soul Builder.
      //
      // 4 sections in vertical order:
      //   1. Soul Manifestation Engine — builder form (name + prompt + tier + submit).
      //      Dispatches `manifest_soul` IPC; Pending→Ready status; persists to
